{"tid":2269190,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Johnny Depp 控告《太陽報》誹謗對前妻動粗一案敗訴","createTime":"2020-11-03T10:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T12:33:38.000Z","uid":118346,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"618ebe43c4524703c7a45e7bbd16eef35d255f95","tid":2269190,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"強尼戴普 (Johnny Depp) 就英國《太陽報》稱他對前妻動粗，是「會打老婆的人」而控告該報誹謗。但《太陽報》稱報導屬實。<br />\n<br />\n11月2日，倫敦法庭就此案公布判決結果，強尼戴普敗訴。法官認為《太陽報》在該篇報導中，證明了事件「基本上真確」。<br />\n<br />\n《太陽報》發言人公開向強尼戴普的前妻道謝，感謝她出庭的「勇氣」。"},{"pid":"2d8e186af87f0403bdd9bffe925cd8902bf142df","tid":2269190,"uid":187232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"What the fuck<br />\n有西真係大哂⋯"},{"pid":"3664411ca3ee9c6ee3a095fe5a9d18fec31c6f60","tid":2269190,"uid":210669,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b83103e26bc63582f17c45183781fb7f8fac51","tid":2269190,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔係一直講Deep先係受害人？屌佢老母條臭閪做乜鳩"},{"pid":"b10515cd2c662fab3e0a26bcf89d5226a7c81b9b","tid":2269190,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"Wtf..."},{"pid":"ff1f603addf9570b9c95175a0efead75e8c731fc","tid":2269190,"uid":314430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"睇Denial<br />\n唔係話英國告誹謗制度係要由<br />\n被告方證明自己冇誹謗<br />\n而非由控告方證明被告有誹謗咩<br />\n<br />\n咁太陽報要證明佢有打女人<br />\n想知有咩證據"},{"pid":"2e408888f77219ef7c2ca9dee817c682df8a3709","tid":2269190,"uid":90460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff1f603addf9570b9c95175a0efead75e8c731fc","tid":2269190,"uid":314430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"睇Denial<br /